                    <h2>Welcome to Encyclopædia Iranica</h2>
                    <p>The Encyclopædia Iranica is a comprehensive research tool dedicated to the study of Iranian civilization in the Middle East, the Caucasus, Central Asia, and the Indian subcontinent.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<div class="button"><a href="/pages/about">LEARN MORE</a></div>&nbsp;<div class="button"><a href="/pages/how-to-search-iranica">WEBSITE FEATURES</a></div></p>
                </div>

