				<h3><a href="/articles/moorey-peter-roger-stuart">MOOREY, Peter Roger Stuart</a></h3> 
				<p>Moorey sat on various administrative bodies and received many distinctions. He was elected a Fellow of the Society of Antiquaries in 1967. Reflecting his involvement with Iranian studies and related fields, he was a member of the Governing Council of the British Institute of Persian Studies.&nbsp;</p>
